										Update Date: 2013.12.27
[How to INSTALL]

Use the "make" command and complete Installation. 

----------------------------------------------------------------

[HOW TO USE]

用法：./mycopy [選項] [檔案......]
選項：
-h                       檢視此輔助說明
-e 檔案1 [檔案2......]   檔案加密（加密後檔案將會附加副檔名.cip）
-d 檔案1 [檔案2......]   檔案解密（解密後檔案將會附加副檔名.txt）
-c 資料夾 資料夾         複製資料夾至目的

----------------------------------------------------------------

[Source Code List]

src/main.c
src/crypt.h src/crypt.c
src/file.h src/file.c

----------------------------------------------------------------

[Method]

1. Copy & Encrypt
	1. Use the linux command "cp" to do the copy. 
	2. Use the linux command "ls" to list all file and director in the target director, and find the "*.txt" file. 
	3. Encrypt the "*.txt" file and make a new file named "*.cip". 
	4. Use the linux command "rm" to remove the "*.txt" file. 
	5. Complete the "Copy & Encrypt" work. 

2. Encrypt
	1. Open the file that need to encrypt. 
	2. Store the text into array. 
	3. Make a new file to store the cipher. 
	4. Do encrypt. 
	5. Store the cipher into the new file. 
	6. Complete the "Encrypt" work. 

3. Decrypt
	1. Open the file that need to decrypt. 
	2. Stor the cipher into array. 
	3. Make a new file to store the text. 
	4. Do decrypt. 
	5. Store the text into the new file. 
	6. Complete the "Decrypt" work. 

4. Help
	1. Check the user's input, if have some error, the help message will appear. 

----------------------------------------------------------------

[Enviroment]

Operating System and Version: Ubuntu 12.10
Linux Kernel Version: 3.5.0-44-generic
GNU coreutils Version: 8.13 

